				\begin{document}$${}^{\cdot }{\rm{O}}{\rm{H}}$$\end{document}O⋅H. Sum up, the Z-scheme heterojunction structure favors the separation of the photo induced electron–hole pairs, with the enhanced photocatalytic activity for N-CDs/P25.Figure 11
